reviewText: Watched this when I was little. Great for popping in and distracting the kids or for bedtime. The eleven different segments makes the replay value high. Sadly, this is hard to get and is only on VHS. If you can get it, go for it.
I used to love this movie
When my oldest was a toddler we discovered Mouse House at the library and checked it out over and over. It's a very sweet British Claymation program, perfect for quiet and restful times.
